@host = http://127.0.0.1:5001

### 1. TEST CONNECTION (Add this first!)
GET {{host}}/api/test

### 2. Register User
POST {{host}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "display_name": "John Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "confirm_password": "123456"
}

### 3. Login
POST {{host}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "123456"
}

### 4. Get Current User
GET {{host}}/api/me

### 5. Logout
POST {{host}}/api/logout

### 6. Try after logout
GET {{host}}/api/me